==暗號==
在每一集結尾處，都有些由[[替換式密碼|取代加密法]]呈現的暗語。

===第一季===
*[[凱撒密碼|凱撒密碼]]：在每集開頭有出現暗示解法的聲音，倒放出來的原句是「往後三個字母」（three letters back）。<ref name="wired">{{cite news|url=http://archive.wired.com/geekdad/2012/09/5-reasons-gravity-falls/|title=Why Gravity Falls Is the Smartest Cartoon on Television|work=Adam Warrock (AKA Z) at Wired.com|accessdate=July 30, 2013|date=September 28, 2012|archive-date=2015-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510075234/http://archive.wired.com/geekdad/2012/09/5-reasons-gravity-falls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在第1～6集出現。
*[[阿特巴希密碼|阿特巴希密碼]]：有些凱撒密碼提示它會在該集被使用；<ref name="wired" />在第7～13集出現。
*[[A1Z26密碼|A1Z26密碼]]：即英文字母換成其出現順序的號碼；在第14～19集出現。
*混合使用：使用多於一種加密法，如：第20集需依序用A1Z26密碼、阿特巴希密碼以及凱撒密碼來解密。第二季的混合密碼則由維吉尼亞密碼開始。
*符號：在季終、日誌裡出現。

===第二季===
*[[维吉尼亚密码|維吉尼亞密碼]]：也在結尾時出現，密鑰會在同一集出現暗示。
*第二季也使用符號密碼。

==迴響==
===評論界===
《神秘小鎮大冒險》曾接受一些公眾人物的評論。

《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的Brian Lowry說：「這個影集品質良好，適合兒童，並讓他們的父母感到懷舊。」<ref>{{cite news|last=Lowry|first=Brian|title=Gravity Falls|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117947746|accessdate=July 8, 2012|publisher=Variety|date=June 12, 2012|archive-date=2012-06-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68QCHklC6?url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117947746|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的Robert Lloyd則說本劇「……相當曲折，有迪士尼的味道，感動人心。」<ref>{{cite news|last=Lloyd|first=Robert|title=Review: Bouncy, weightless fun with 'Gravity Falls'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-gravity-falls-20120613,0,2624952.story?track=rss|accessdate=July 8, 2012|publisher=Los Angeles Times|date=June 11, 2012|archive-date=2020-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200526213350/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-xpm-2012-jun-15-la-et-gravity-falls-20120613-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在他的報導裡，《紐約每日新聞》的David Hinckley認為神秘小鎮大冒險「不同凡響而可愛」並讚美美寶這個角色。<ref>{{cite news|last=Hinckley|first=David|title=New animated Disney series 'Gravity Falls' rises to an endearing level of tween cool|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/television/new-animated-disney-series-gravity-falls-rises-endearing-level-tween-cool-article-1.1104162|accessdate=July 8, 2012|publisher=New York Daily News|date=June 29, 2012|archive-date=2012-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120702151209/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/television/new-animated-disney-series-gravity-falls-rises-endearing-level-tween-cool-article-1.1104162|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[連線|連線]]》的Matt Blum則將其與《[[天兵公園|天兵公園]]》、《[[飛哥與小佛|飛哥與小佛]]》相媲美，盛讚道「機智、奇特並有幾分深沉」。<ref>{{cite news|last=Blum|first=Matt|title=Gravity Falls Rises to the Level of Disney Channel’s Best|url=https://www.wired.com/geekdad/2012/06/gravity-falls-disney/|accessdate=July 8, 2012|publisher=Wired Magazine|date=June 28, 2012|archive-date=2012-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704220505/http://www.wired.com/geekdad/2012/06/gravity-falls-disney|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[富比士|富比士]]》Erik Kain稱《神秘小鎮大冒險》為「當下電視（節目中）最棒的」；<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2015/08/27/gravity-falls-is-the-best-show-on-television/|title='Gravity Falls' Is The Best Show On Television|publisher=Forbes.com|date=August 27, 2015|accessdate=August 28, 2015|first=Erik|last=Kain|archive-date=2015-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150830001406/http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2015/08/27/gravity-falls-is-the-best-show-on-television/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[紐約郵報|紐約郵報]]》的Kayla Cobb更說《神秘小鎮大冒險》是「有史以來幾個結構上最精巧的電視劇之一」。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://decider.com/2016/10/18/cult-corner-gravity-falls/|title='Gravity Falls' is one of the most structurally smart shows ever created|publisher=Decider.com|date=October 18, 2016|first=Kayla|last=Cobb|accessdate=2018-02-21|archive-date=2017-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302113020/https://decider.com/2016/10/18/cult-corner-gravity-falls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

